### Ask about a mission (will trigger tool call)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/chat/spy-007
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "What happened during the Paris mission?",
  "tool_calls": [
    {
      "name": "get_mission_context",
      "arguments": {"mission_id": "paris"}
    }
  ]
}

